{"tid":2267663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保就業結束 恐僱主「換血」 勞處空缺增 羅致光奢談復蘇","createTime":"2020-11-02T08:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:52:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f307e9f4be19695ad75c24af3613c09ac583321","tid":2267663,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/LILAHIJUMVG4VF6USLCYZAUB3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FLILAHIJUMVG4VF6USLCYZAUB3Y%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=9f6dd653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FLILAHIJUMVG4VF6USLCYZAUB3Y%2F&h=d990647f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/LILAHIJUMVG4VF6USLCYZAUB3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保就業結束 恐僱主「換血」<br />\n勞處空缺增 羅致光奢談復蘇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CmEEJnYCXLCwmJkIKKLvctJ9dkw=/854x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IHVBONBDMBEA7LMWIHNQQ7A5M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCmEEJnYCXLCwmJkIKKLvctJ9dkw%3D%2F854x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIHVBONBDMBEA7LMWIHNQQ7A5M4.jpg&h=b3021663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅致光<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情下，本港失業率高企，近日更有多間大企業宣佈裁員或要求員工停薪留職。惟勞工及福利局局長羅致光漠視現況，吹噓本港就業市場正向好發展，聲稱香港疫情9月開始紓緩，勞工巿場有穩定迹象，指不少經濟指標亦「谷底回升」，勞工處9月份接獲的職位空缺更按月大增八成。有工會直斥羅致光選擇性公佈數字，漠視不少公司正實施「換血」行動，提醒不少企業正部署在保就業計劃本月完結後裁員，本港勞動市場「有排未見到谷底」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：兩成畢業青年疫下冇工開<br />\n<br />\n政府防疫漏洞導致第三波疫情重創本港經濟，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱經濟指標回升<br />\n<br />\n惟勞福局長羅致光昨透過網誌表示，雖本港失業率仍高企，第三季失業人數超過25萬，但疫情9月起已紓緩，勞工巿場有穩定下來的迹象，不少經濟指標「谷底回升」。他引述勞工處今年9月從私營機構接獲的職位空缺數目為78,578個，比8月份低位43,725個職缺大幅上升79.7%。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光特別提到安老服務人力短缺問題，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又稱，政府2018年12月成立十億元樂齡及康復創科應用基金，資助合資格的安老及康復服務單位購置、租借或試用科技產品。基金至今三個批次合共批出超過兩億元，資助約970個安老及康復服務單位購置或租用逾4,200件科技產品。基金第四批次申請今日截止。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟副主席張麗霞不認同勞工巿場已穩定下來，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職工盟：有排未見底<br />\n<br />\n她又透露，工會最近接獲裁員求助個案增加，除了中小企，亦涉及跨國企業，部份企業則選擇要求員工放無薪假，「叫員工一個星期返三、四日，因為未符合停工嘅定義，員工被迫長期吊鹽水，公司又唔使支付遣散賠償。」由於補貼僱主出糧的保就業計劃，在發放11月份資助後將結束，張預計就業情況只會更加惡劣，失業、就業不足及低工資問題將持續一段長時間，「有排未見到谷底」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0u6MO4WFriDaUCUsFqUprt-zGg0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DQ4QPRRNYNFJ3OYRWCX2YU4GSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0u6MO4WFriDaUCUsFqUprt-zGg0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDQ4QPRRNYNFJ3OYRWCX2YU4GSU.jpg&h=aecd3f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張麗霞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pLjxA5WjTgVJwOiiDAcYCtKzTfs=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JG32X2L4MFEOVCYQHWQ4ODPAPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpLjxA5WjTgVJwOiiDAcYCtKzTfs%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJG32X2L4MFEOVCYQHWQ4ODPAPY.jpg&h=f52bb013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疫情打擊下本港經濟重創，失業率高企。"},{"pid":"190f2988a3bda0f4c132604198d98dd87a371fa2","tid":2267663,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"其實除左講職位空缺數目，都要講埋人工。依家d公司會用低人工請人，請到就炒舊人。"}]}